面会介绍到）配合工作。\")]),t._v(\" \"),t._m(74),t._v(\" \"),t._m(75),t._v(\" \"),t._m(76),t._v(\" \"),t._m(77),t._v(\" \"),t._m(78),t._m(79),t._v(\" \"),t._m(80),t._v(\" \"),t._m(81),t._v(\" \"),t._m(82),t._v(\" \"),t._m(83),t._v(\" \"),t._m(84),t._v(\" \"),t._m(85),t._v(\" \"),t._m(86),t._v(\" \"),t._m(87),t._v(\" \"),t._m(88),t._v(\" \"),t._m(89),t._v(\" \"),t._m(90),t._v(\" \"),t._m(91),t._v(\" \"),t._m(92),t._v(\" \"),t._m(93),t._v(\" \"),t._m(94),t._v(\" \"),e(\"p\",[t._v(\"被视为JDK1.7中HotSpot虚拟机的一个重要进化特征。它具备一下特点：\")]),t._v(\" \"),t._m(95),t._v(\" \"),e(\"p\",[t._v(\"G1收集器的运作大致分为以下几个步骤：\")]),t._v(\" \"),t._m(96),t._v(\" \"),t._m(97),t._v(\" \"),e(\"p\",[t._v(\"参考：\")]),t._v(\" \"),t._m(98)])},[function(){var t=this.$createElement,s=this._self._c||t;return s(\"h2\",{attrs:{id:\"写在前面\"}},[s(\"a\",{staticClass:\"header-anchor\",attrs:{href:\"#写在前面\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\"}},[this._v(\"#\")]),this._v(\" 写在前面\")])},function(){var t=this.$createElement,s=this._self._c||t;return s(\"h3\",{attrs:{id:\"本节常见面试题：\"}},[s(\"a\",{staticClass:\"header-anchor\",attrs:{href:\"#本节常见面试题：\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\"}},[this._v(\"#\")]),this._v(\" 本节常见面试题：\")])},function(){var t=this,s=t.$createElement,e=t._self._c||s;return e(\"ul\",[e(\"li\",[t._v(\"如何判断对象是否死亡（两种方法）。\")]),t._v(\" \"),e(\"li\",[t._v(\"简单的介绍一下强引用、软引用、弱引用、虚引用（虚引用与软引用和弱引用的区别、使用软引用能带来的好处）。\")]),t._v(\" \"),e(\"li\",[t._v(\"如何判断一个常量是废弃常量\")]),t._v(\" \"),e(\"li\",[t._v(\"如何判断一个类是无用的类\")]),t._v(\" \"),e(\"li\",[t._v(\"垃圾收集有哪些算法，各自的特点？\")]),t._v(\" \"),e(\"li\",[t._v(\"HotSpot为什么要分为新生代和老年代？\")]),t._v(\" \"),e(\"li\",[t._v(\"常见的垃圾回收器有那些？\")]),t._v(\" \"),e(\"li\",[t._v(\"介绍一下CMS,G1收集器。\")]),t._v(\" \"),e(\"li\",[t._v(\"Minor Gc和Full GC 有什么不同呢？\")])])},function(){var t=this.$createElement,s=this._self._c||t;return s(\"h3\",{attrs:{id:\"本文导火索\"}},[s(\"a\",{staticClass:\"header-anchor\",attrs:{href:\"#本文导火索\",\"aria-hidden\":\"true\"}},[this._v(\"#\")]),this._v(\" 本文导火索\")])},function(){var t=this.$createElement,s=this._self._c||t;retu